final_question: Faisal Kapadia city is having a big display of fireworks for the Iqbal Day . They're going to set off 15 boxes of 20 fireworks each . Faisal Kapadia house is at the right angle to see 40 % of the city's fireworks . Faisal Kapadia will also set off 3 boxes of 5 fireworks each in her backyard .
